  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Marble Mash is a fast-paced arcade style clicker game where you try to rack up as many points as you can in a round.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each round you are faced with the challenge of trying to click the blue marbles and avoiding the red ones. The pressure builds as gold marbles get thrown into the mix which earn you extra points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game also features a leader board so you can compete to rise to the top!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to be the Marble Mash champion?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Marble Mash is a fast-paced arcade style clicker game where you try to rack up as many points as you can in a round.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each round you are faced with the challenge of trying to click the blue marbles and avoiding the red ones. The pressure builds as gold marbles get thrown into the mix which earn you extra points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game also features a leader board so you can compete to rise to the top!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to be the Marble Mash champion?</p>",
